HEADWORD: Manumotor
<hw>Man"u*mo`tor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>manus</ets> the hand + E. <ets>motor</ets>.]</ety> <def>A small
wheel carriage, so constructed that a person sitting in it may move
it.</def>⟦br⟧
